              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Experimental elemental yields were obtained by Gaussian",
                "fitting of the independent yields for the isotope",
                "chains of Cu, Zn, Ga and Ge. Due to the lack of",
                "experimental data, the value for Ni was estimated",
                "using the experimental yield of 71Ni only and the",
                "theoretical value of the average mass equal 71.23",
                "and the mass dispersion equal 1.47, for the Ni-chain."
